1. Nge e Nzambi ampungu, wavelela beni,
\nTukuyimbidila nsung’a kembela.
\nNgeye u Nkwa nkenda, Nzambi a ngolo zingi,
\nEse, yo Mwana, yo Mwand’avelela.
\n
\n2. Aya bena koko bekukundang’aka;
\nOko lose luaku bekukembela;
\nAmbasi yo wantu bekuvuminanga;
\nNgeye i Nzambi anzingi kikilu.
\n
\n3. Nge e Mfumu Nzambi walungila mwawosono;
\nKana vo kw’asumuki olembi moneka;
\nNge i Nzambi ansongi, osundidi awonso;
\nNge amosi kaka i Nzambi avelela.
\n
\n4. Nge e Nzambi ampungu a walakazi wingi;
\nE vangwa yaku nkutu mpe yau ikukembela.
\nNgeye u Nkwa nkanka, Nzambi a ngolo zingi,
\nEse, yo Mwana, yo Mwand’avelela.
\n
